                <h1>Welcome to <span>Briarwood Manor</span></h1>
                <p>Personal Care with a Personal Touch is not just our motto it’s our way of life.</p>
                <p>We put your safety and comfort first!</p>
                <p><img src="images/group-shot.png" alt="Briarwood Manor" title="Briarwood Manor" class="right"><strong>Briarwood Manor</strong> is a short-term and long-term personal care facility, serving individuals, couples, and their families in the Newfoundland, Pennsylvania area. We strive for excellence in everything we do, and consistently put the safety and comfort of you or your loved ones at the top of our list. Our highly trained staff members are available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, always keeping the happiness of each and every resident top of mind. </p>
                <p><strong class="txt-1">What We Do</strong></p>
                <p>Our turn of the century campus is designed to instill a warm sense of pride in our residents, and our one-of-a-kind facility gives residents a place they want to be, rather than a place they have to be. Our manicured landscaping is an inviting place to admire nature, and the changing seasons bring with them fireside dinners, festive celebrations, and memories that will last a lifetime.</p>
                <p><img src="images/thankgiving.png" alt="Briarwood Manor" title="Briarwood Manor" class="left"><strong class="txt-1">Open House</strong></p>
                <p>We invite you to come view our newly renovated historic campus any day of the week. Please contact us at 570-252-4224 or info@briarwoodmanorpa.com before your visit for a private interview or showing, or to schedule a needs assessment for you or your loved one.</p>
